rows.label: qst700104_msg0001
rows.name: Well hello there... You must be Yonma.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0002
rows.name: Come on, it's all right. You're safe now.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0101
rows.name:
Don't be afraid.
Just come with us.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0201
rows.name: Hi, Yonma. We've been looking for you.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0302
rows.name:
Erm... Ajijii? No, Yonma, was it?
Come on, time to go.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0401
rows.name:
Found you...
Come on, you're coming with us.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0402
rows.name: And no back talk, you hear me?

rows.label: qst700104_msg0502
rows.name:
...What a handsome beast you are.
Come along now.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0602
rows.name: Don't be scared. We'll get you home.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0702
rows.name:
Time to come home now.
There's a good girl.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0801
rows.name: We have been searching for you.

rows.label: qst700104_msg0802
rows.name:
I'm Wadatsumi, and I have sworn
on my honor to return you to your master.
